title: One Hit Wonder Game! + Can Amy Dial The Phone With Her Feet? + Lunchbox Prank Calls Dairy Queen!
itunes:title: One Hit Wonder Game! + Can Amy Dial The Phone With Her Feet? + Lunchbox Prank Calls Dairy Queen!
description:
Bobby plays song clips from various one hit wonder artists/bands and the show members have to try and guess them. A recent news story involved a woman saving herself from trouble by dialing for help with her feet...so we put Amy to the same test in the studio! Plus, Lunchbox prank calls Dairy Queen to see just what kind of animals they're putting in their animal blizzards!
